163
00:07:46,860 --> 00:07:48,260
When the results
of the literacy test come out,

164
00:07:48,340 --> 00:07:49,340
you will be

165
00:07:49,420 --> 00:07:50,820
the Crown Princess.

166
00:07:51,980 --> 00:07:52,780
Look.

167
00:07:53,020 --> 00:07:55,060
