168
00:07:55,180 --> 00:07:56,780
We only need to wait
for mother's order of coronation.

169
00:07:57,180 --> 00:07:57,980
Presents?

170
00:07:58,580 --> 00:07:59,460
For me?

171
00:07:59,740 --> 00:08:02,180
