211
00:09:48,100 --> 00:09:48,940
Qianqian.

212
00:09:49,380 --> 00:09:51,500
You have been intelligent
and diligent since childhood.

213
00:09:51,540 --> 00:09:53,300
I always have great expectations for you.

214
00:09:53,340 --> 00:09:54,940
