267
00:11:43,820 --> 00:11:44,500
You. You...

268
00:11:44,540 --> 00:11:46,300
You are the so-called braggers.

269
00:11:46,340 --> 00:11:47,900
You do nothing except

270
00:11:47,980 --> 00:11:49,100
